Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:18.41,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Does the light of the sky reach your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:28.30,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}The melody we dreamed of was serene.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:33.40,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Even though the dream is so far from you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:38.42,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Try to recall that gentle voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:51.23,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Someone's singing a graceful chord for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:55.60,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}May the sound of the skies resound,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:01:00.61,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}overcoming sadness with all its might.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.69,0:01:11.21,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Only the real world reflects in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:20.60,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Don't let your tears form any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:25.89,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Within the overflowing light,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:32.87,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}may you play out the morrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:51.06,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Let's get friendship, love, and other feelings together,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:54.43,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}and play out how important they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.61,0:23:12.34,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}I cried from joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:18.36,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}I laughed from pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:24.34,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}But that's all a part of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:27.16,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}and tells me that I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:31.78,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Let's take this slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.54,0:23:33.36,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:37.87,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Can you tell me how you really feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:39.06,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}You're just my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:44.71,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Even when friendship and love waver,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:44.90,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}I know, you know, will be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:50.68,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}I hope this melody will ring forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:50.82,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Can you count my precious flower
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:56.82,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Overflowing words are hardly enough to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:24:02.69,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}This is our harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:07.65,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Can you hear our harmony?
