Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That noise would wake the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:55.15,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\blur0.5\fs75\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\fnBurst My Bubble KK\b1}A Day with the Squad {\fnArial}•{\fnBurst My Bubble KK} Rio Runs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This is yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dish native to my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this "miso" the stuff that's\Nmade the same way as soy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a bit of miso\Nmy mom made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty more,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Treize?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally received notification\Nabout more supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking Kureha\Nto pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running low on ammunition, medicine,\Nand a lot of everyday supplies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be all right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carl's studio, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're spending the whole\Nafternoon practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grub's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What horrible manners...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad would cry\Nif he saw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like them, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't the kids at the\Nchurch's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demanding money to spread\Ntheir useless superstitions...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as everywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are good cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.61,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems like she's\Nreally fitting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute how hard\Nshe always tries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit she's serious\Nand fired-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But things out here aren't easy enough\Nto get by on those qualities alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that look mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.61,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Horrible Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, see you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cause trouble\Nfor Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Setting sail...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't expect you to\Nbe able to do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you should be able to control the\Nsound using only the mouthpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you finding\Nlife at the base?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so easygoing\Nabout everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nwhy did you join the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I heard I could learn to\Nplay an instrument for free...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I understand that p-protecting\Nthe country is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care whether it was\Nfor money or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those with a distinct goal in mind last longer\Nthan those who just kind of joined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why did you join, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess for the opposite\Nof your reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's rare these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost never hear brass instruments\Noutside of the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sound like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sound of the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot. It's hot, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK... It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want some snow to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK. Just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow... Where's the snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell would we\Nhave any snow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. That's a last resort!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine, medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine! Medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...running low on a\Nlot of stuff, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those idiots in\Nthe Supply Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the children cause\Nproblems again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me for my rudeness\Nup until this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a bit of high fever,\Nbut this should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something really bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's malaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malaria? Only kids get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even adults can get it\Nif they're very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of kids get it right\Nafter we take them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more they appear to be fine,\Nthe worse it is when it hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was fighting it off the whole time, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then... Will she get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't stay like this forever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is infused with herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to her a little later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serving the people of this town\Nis our joy and our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May all blessings be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your cooperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an {\i1}omiso{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stuff we had this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miso dregs...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you make miso soup,\Nyou strain the miso...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leftover beans,\Nand stuff from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good-for-nothing, useless,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been like that,\Never since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought that this time, I'd work\Nreally hard and not trouble anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a lot more fragile\Nthan you looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a selfish, spoiled kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did... Did I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That song you were singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She only heard it one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't the first\Ntime I'd heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to play it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That song sounded like it was\Ncoming down from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess once an omiso,\Nalways an omiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just rely on the\Nchurch for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemikazuchi is a\Nrelic from a past era.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a lot of things are\Nsleeping inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Ask Noel for the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This song!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably what that song\Nsounds like complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of instruments, all playing in harmony,\Nbecoming one piece of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as a tank crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, gunner, driver,\Nand communications...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone works together\Nto operate one tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every part is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every sound is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just something I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the person I respect and\Nadmire more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To borrow her words...\NKanata, why do you think superior officers exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So their juniors can cause\Nproblems for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you can't do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just remember how much it hurt,\Nhow powerless it felt,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and how happy you were\Nto be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And someday, when you're in the position\Nto protect someone, it will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cause as much trouble\Nfor me as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if you screw up,\Nyou'll be scolded and punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... If it hurts, say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're suffering, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to cause lots and\Nlots of trouble for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go easy on me, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... I should've stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata got Rio\Nto nurse her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It was no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she was just tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be fine if she sleeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemikazuchi's lights were on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I used it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listened to that\Nsong, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you never would again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just really wanted to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
